'''《极速前进19》'''（{{lang|en|'''''The Amazing Race 19'''''}}）是流行[[真人秀|真人秀]]節目《[[极速前进|极速前进]]》的第十九季。本季會繼續有十一對有各種既定關係的參賽者，為最終大獎——一百萬美元進行環球旅行競賽<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cbs.com/casting/amazing_race/Application_Form.pdf|title=報名表格（Application  form）|author=CBS.com|accessdate=2010-01-22|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100602071033/http://www.cbs.com/casting/amazing_race/Application_Form.pdf|archivedate=2010-06-02}}</ref>。

本季賽事之報名於2011年1月4日結束，準入圍者面試會於同年3月中舉行，最終面試於[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]舉行，而節目的攝製於2011年的春季或夏季進行<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cbs.com/casting/amazing_race/Eligibility_Requirements.pdf|title=資格要求（Eligibility Requirements）|author=CBS.com|accessdate=2011-01-22|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090407080105/http://www.cbs.com/casting/amazing_race/Eligibility_Requirements.pdf|archivedate=2009-04-07}}</ref>。极速前进19於2011年9月25日在[[哥倫比亞廣播公司|哥倫比亞廣播公司]]（CBS）電視台首播。<ref name="TVByTheNumbers">{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2011/08/31/cbs-announces-the-cast-for-the-new-season-of-the-amazing-race-premiering-sunday-sept-25/101916/|title=CBS Announces The Cast For The New Season Of "The Amazing Race," Premiering Sunday, Sept. 25|last=Gorman|first=Bill|publisher=TV By The Numbers|date=2011-08-31|accessdate=2011-09-01|archive-date=2011-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110923115133/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2011/08/31/cbs-announces-the-cast-for-the-new-season-of-the-amazing-race-premiering-sunday-sept-25/101916/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

